Job Responsibilities :

Translate financial document such as IPO prospectuses, shareholders’ circulars, annual and interim reports and associated press announcements;
Translate legal documents such as legal contracts and agreements;
Translate any other commercial documents assigned by the Company from time to time; and
Any other duties as delegated by Company.

