University graduate in Translation or related disciplines;
2 years of relevant translation experience in financial, legal or related industry is preferred;
Good command of both written English and Chinese;
Flexibility to work overtime to meet tight deadlines is preferred;
Good interpersonal skill;
Willing to take shift duty;
Candidate with more experience will be considered as Senior Translator; and
Fresh graduate will also be considered.

